dbQuery.sql:
SELECT FAC.METER_ID, sum(FAC.DP_CHARGE_AMOUNT) AS FACIL_CHARGE_AMT FROM WBISCCD.DELIVERY_PT_BILLING_CHARGES FAC , WBISCCD.RATE_CHARGE_DEFINITION DEF
WHERE FAC.STOPDATE IS NULL
AND FAC.DP_CHARGE_DESC = DEF.ID AND UPPER(DEF.DEFINITION_TEXT) = 'FACILITY CHARGE' GROUP BY FAC.METER_ID

SELECT A.VOL_TYPE, A.DAY AS DAY, A.HOUR/100 AS HOUR, SUM(A.ALLOCATED_VALUE) AS SEPA_KWH FROM WBISCCD.SEPA_INTERVAL_ALLOCATION A WHERE A.CUSTOMER_ID = '002800000107'
GROUP BY A.DAY, A.HOUR,A.VOL_TYPE
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID, DAY, HOUR, SUM(TOTAL_DISPATCH_KWH) AS TOTAL_DISPATCH FROM WBISCCD.VMEA_30MIN_CALL GROUP BY CUSTOMER_ID, DAY, HOUR

Peak Date
queryItem.expression: decode([Business Layer].[Wholesale Customer].[On Peak Flag] ,1,to_char([Business Layer].[Wholesale Customer].[Customer On Peak Date],'MM/DD/YYYY'),to_char([Business Layer].[Wholesale Customer].[Customer Off Peak Date],'MM/DD/YYYY'))

queryItem.name: Peak Time
queryItem.expression: decode([Business Layer].[Wholesale Customer].[On Peak Flag] ,1,to_char([Business Layer].[Wholesale Customer].[Customer On Peak Date],'HH24:MI'),to_char([Business Layer].[Wholesale Customer].[Customer Off Peak Date],'HH24:MI'))

queryItem.name: Service Peak
queryItem.expression: decode([Business Layer].[Wholesale Customer].[On Peak Flag] ,1,[Business Layer].[Wholesale Customer].[Customer On Peak KW] ,[Business Layer].[Wholesale Customer].[Customer Off Peak KW] )

queryItem.name: Total MW
queryItem.expression: ([Business Layer].[VMEA Appendix D].[Gen Turbine Load] + [Business Layer].[VMEA Appendix D].[Gen Diesel Load] )/1000
